  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Core Gameplay</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Move your army of soldiers left or right with the mouse.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Encounter wooden signs to increase your troops based on the numbers shown, quickly growing your army!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Strategize every move—choose the most rewarding path!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >When facing enemy soldiers, overpower them with superior numbers to advance!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Lead your army to break through obstacles and reach the goal.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Key Features</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > No ads in the game.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Enhances quick calculation skills through strategic play.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Use springboards to make your army leap forward!</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Core Gameplay</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Move your army of soldiers left or right with the mouse.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Encounter wooden signs to increase your troops based on the numbers shown, quickly growing your army!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Strategize every move—choose the most rewarding path!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >When facing enemy soldiers, overpower them with superior numbers to advance!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Lead your army to break through obstacles and reach the goal.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Key Features</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > No ads in the game.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Enhances quick calculation skills through strategic play.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Use springboards to make your army leap forward!</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
